Abstract: Tigera is the team behind Project Calico, the most popular open-sou

body.content:
Title: aisU Level Up: Introduction to Tigera and Calico for Kubernetes/AKS  


Presenters: Yared Tsegaye, Solution Director, Apaar Sharma, and Peter Marini from Tigera 


Abstract: Tigera is the team behind Project Calico, the most popular open-source network and network policy solution for Kubernetes, including Microsoft Azure Kubernetes Service (AKS).  This session will introduce the enhancements that Calico provides to the AKS platform as well as the capabilities of Tigera's commercial offerings Calico Enterprise and Calico Cloud, a cloud-native application protection platform. 

Learning Objectives: 

  • How the Kubernetes networking model (particularly in AKS) presents new challenges 

  • The capabilities that Calico (open source and commercial) provide  

Target Audience: Anyone interested in AKS or Kubernetes in general 

  

Charge Code Guidance: 20002-001-013 TM-aisU series with a comment, aisU Level Up  

 

Interested in leading a future session or have a topic suggestion:  Please contact aisU@ais.com
